description: Number of partitions of n into 6 positive cubes.
maple: A025459 := proc(n)    local a,x,y,z,u,v,wcu ;    a := 0 ;    for x from 1 do        if 6*x^3 > n then            return a;        end if;        for y from x do            if x^3+5*y^3 > n then                break;            end if;            for z from y do                if x^3+y^3+4*z^3 > n then                    break;                end if;                for u from z do                    if x^3+y^3+z^3+3*u^3 > n then                        break;                    end if;                    for v from u do                        if x^3+y^3+z^3+u^3+2*v^3 > n then                            break;                        end if;                        wcu := n-x^3-y^3-z^3-u^3-v^3 ;                        if isA000578(wcu) then                            a := a+1 ;                        end if;                    end do:                end do:            end do:        end do:    end do:end proc: # _R.
